# Readme

## Setup

Clone this repository

```
git clone ...
```

Install requirements

```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Then, edit the configuration in the minitwit.py file or export an MINITWIT_SETTINGS environment variable pointing to a configuration file.

Fire up a shell and run this

```
flask --app=minitwit initdb
```

Now you can run:

```
flask --app=minitwit run
```

Check out http://localhost:5000/
